episodes.title: Phone Call With Scientology Staff Member
episodes.description: I am making this post as a protest against the cult I was born and raised in. This call was made from a single-party-consent state to another single-party-consent state, making it fully legal. Scientology is a destructive, family-destroying, human-trafficking cult that has no place in a free society. This is the truth, from an actual Scientologist, that Scientology doesn't want you to hear.
